	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hey!!! I get to add to the pile of "maybe, if, maybe not".. hahahaha gotta love it. K, here's the deal.<br><br>All weapons have a damage bonus. Not innate to the weapon, innate to the characters level & skill level (or maybe just their level).<br><br>The damage bonus showing on a rusty weapon, or a baton of faith, is just that. Do not confuse yourself. At some unknown level the baton of faith showed a 5damage bonus, and some SK in my group had a mithril 2her that also shown 5dmg bonus. Now my monk is level 49 and the baton of faith has more damage bonus on it, 7, or something.. the point is, it changes. Because it is level and/or skill level dependant, it is NOT the recent upgrade with increases damage bonuses to 2 handed weapons.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
